name: Digital Blue Carabiner Digital Camera-Pink
description:
Digital Blue Snap Digital Camera
VGA 640×480 resolution
Fixed Focus
Holds up to 40 pictures on internal memory
Spring loaded clip for easy attachment to belts, bags, and jackets
LCD Frame Counter (photo counter only, not an image display)
Operates on 1 AAA battery (Not Included)
USB Cable
Photo Editing software
Unit Dimensions: 4.125”L x 2.5”W x .75”H
Weight: 1.9oz

name: Argus Bean Sprout Carabiner Digital Camera
description:
Resolution: 300K Pixels (640×480) VGA
Versatile clip-on design prevents loss
LCD display with total picture count on back of camera
Water resistant
Lead free RoHS compliant
Lens: Non-Spherical Lens f=5.4mm
Aperture: 1:2.6
Focusing range: 0.5m-infinity
Storage capacity: 2MB
Photo storage: Up to 26 high-resolution (640×480 pixels), Up to 52 compressed high resolution photos, Up to 104 low-resolution (320×240 pixels), Up to 208 compressed low-resolution photos
Power supply: Lithium battery (built-in) or USB cable
Charge: By USB cable
USB Transfer/Charging Cable
ArcSoft Photoimpression 4 and driver installation CD
Bean Sprout Wristband
